Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 那边真的很热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是里见或尾崎带进来的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好奇那个莉芳特意邀请来的重要客人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.56,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.56,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:48.06,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:48.06,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:54.36,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:54.36,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹着干燥的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:01:00.82,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:01:00.82,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真伪 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:04.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:04.24,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈愿待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:06.96,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:06.96,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱过 恨过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲伤最后化作温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:15.46,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:15.46,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:20.30,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:20.30,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍会寻觅明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:24.43,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:24.43,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃烧的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:29.56,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:29.56,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之缘 最终转化成奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.61,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.61,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.19,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.19,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:37.49,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:37.49,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拨开黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:41.66,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:41.66,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追寻你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:47.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:47.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总有一天 命运将会转变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:52.21,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:52.21,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让眼泪白流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:56.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:56.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交织骚动的尽头
